h1. BetterMigrations

h2. Installation

<code>
sudo gem install rails-better-migrations
</code>

h2. Undoing migrations

Run @rake db:migrate:undo@ and select a migration to undo.

h2. Applying migrations

Run @rake db:migrate:do@ and select a migration to apply.

